sentences: Delegates discussed the New Delhi Work Programme relating to UNFCCC Article 6 ( FCCC/SBI/2007/MISC.3 and Add.1).
KENYA noted lack of financial resources, and UNEP, CBD and CMS outlined their activities.
enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
